    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels at Model Risk Level 2. The output comparison factor is satisfied by CFD-predicted RH values below 1.0 across all operating points. The team accepted the simulation sweep as providing equivalent discriminatory power to a physical hemolysis experiment, given the well-characterised FDA pump geometry and the independently validated hemolysis constitutive model. The six non-assessed factors are within the scope exclusions permitted at MRL 2. The overall credibility body of evidence is judged sufficient to support the intended use decision.",
